      • appleCatchCount

        public void appleCatchCount()
        Every time an apples is collected this method is called. When an instance of the SpawnApple class is collected, this method is called and increments the totalCount variable and increments the appleCount variable as well

      • melonCatchCount

        public void melonCatchCount()
        Every time a melon is collected this method is called. When an instance of the SpawnWatermelon class is collected, this method is called and increments the totalCount variable by two, as collecting a melon is worth 2 points, and increments the melonCount variable as well

      • getRottenCount

        public int getRottenCount()
        Returns the total number of rotten apples collected
        Returns:
        rottenCount

      • rottenCatchCount

        public void rottenCatchCount()
        Every time a rotten apple is collected this method is called. When an instance of the SpawnRottenApple class is collected, this method is called and decrements the totalCount variable, as collecting a rotten apples is worth negative points, and the rottenCount is also incremented.
